      Dootle is a fork of the Tootle Client for Mastodon, to better support the Gnome Desktop and other GTK desktops not named "Pantheon".
    </p>
    <p>
      Dootle is designed with the Mastodon API in mind and should support any Fediverse Server that implements it.
